original_title: Sri Lanka bonds closes steady, rupee 325.75/326.00 to dollar
original_body_lines: ECONOMYNEXT – Sri Lanka bonds closed steady, dealers said while the spot US dollar closed at 325.75/326.00 rupees.
A bond maturing on 15.05.2030 closed at 15.90/16.00 percent unchanged from opening.
A bond maturing on 15.01.2028 closed at 15.10/15 percent unchanged from opening.
A bond maturing on 15.09.2027 closed steady at 13.30/40 percent after opening at 13.25/50 percent.
A bond maturing on 15.05.2026 closed at 14.30/15.40, after not being quoted for 7 sessions and 01.07.2025 closed at 14.80/15.10. (Colombo/July19/2023)
